HEADWORD: Bomber jacket
<hw>Bom"ber jack`et</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From its
resemblance to the style of jacket work by the crews of World War II
bomber airplanes.]</ety> <def>a short men's jacket made of leather,
having a zipper in front, knitted cuffs, and ribbed trim.</def>⟦br⟧
